Feature: Remove Meetup
    In order to remove a meetup
    As a anonymous user
    I want to be able to change information about a meetup on the application

Scenario: I remove a meetup
    Given I am on the meetup's remove page
    When I click on the button "Supprimer"
    Then I should be redirect to the list of meetups without the meetup I deleted

Scenario: I remove a meetup
    Given I am on the meetup's remove page
    When I click on the button "Non"
    Then I should be redirect to the list of meetups with the meetup I selected
